description: What is Kiki's Playground?  A collective that is open to all artists for finding creative inspiration, learning how to collaborate, and being a part of a fun community!  Create what inspires you when you think about Kiki, sort of like Kiki fan art! Kiki lists as Kiki's Playground and pays all minting fees.  The cut is 90/10 with the artist keeping the majority, always!
